{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "N tee Wilistexi karroja\nprett Israëlu/ un Isra-\netā Wiḣri behdse preeḱsch\nteem Wilistereem/ un kritte no-\nkauti us to Kalnu Gilboa.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet tee Wilisteri laufsbs\nus Saulu/ un us winna Deh-\nleem/ un tee Wilisteri nokawe\nJonatanu/ un Abinadabu / un\nMaltisũĩ/ Saula Dehlus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un ta Kauschana bija brees-\nmiga prett Saulu/un tee Strehl-\nneeki aisnehme winnu ar sawcem\nStohpeim/ ka winch no teem\nStrehlneekem eewainohts ktua.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Sauls us fa-\nwu Bruzzu-Neffejn: Jsweiz\ntawu Sobbinu/ un nodurr man\nar to/ ka fchee Neapgraisiti ne\nnaht un maun Smecklā leek. Bet\nwinna Bruzzu-Neffejs ne grib-\nbeja/ jo winch bihjajahs tohti.\nTad nehme Sauls to Sobbinu/\nun mettehs us to.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kad nu winna Bruzzu-\nNeffejs redseja/ ka Sauls bija\nnomirris/ tad mettehs winch ar-\nri Sobbinā/ un nomirre.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta nomirre Sauls / un\nwinna trihs Dehli/ un wiṣ win-\nna Nams nomirre fohpā.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kad nu wiṣi Israëta Wiḣ-\nri/ kas Eeleijā bija/ redseja/ ku\ntee behdse/ un ka Sauls un win-\nna Dehli bija nomirruscht/ tad\npanette tee ṣawus Pilsfahns/\nun behdse/ un tee Wilisteri nah-\nze/ un dshwoja eekṭch teem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un ohtrā Deenā nahze tee\nWilisteri tohs Nokautus aptau-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "piht/ un atradde Saulu un\nwinna Dehlus us Gilboas Kal-\nnu gullim/\n9. Un tee iswilke tain Dreh-\nbes/ un pazehle winna Galwu\nun winna Bruzzas/ un fuhttija\ntohs Wilisteru Senmē apkahrt/\nka tas isteikts taptu ṣawu Elka-\nDeewu Nammā/ un starp teem\nGaudim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "10. Un tee nolikke winna\nBruzzas ṣawā Deewa Nam-\nnā/ un winna Galwu peekalle\ntee pee Dagoxa Namma.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "11. Kad nu wiṣi Jabeṣā eeksch\nGileadas dsirdeja/ wiṣu/ ko tee\nWilisteri Saulam bij darrijschi/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "12. Tad zehlahs wiṣi spehzī-\ngi Wiḣri/ un nehme Saula Mee-\nfas/ un winna Dehlu Meefas/\nun nehfe tahs us Jabeṣu/ un ap-\nratke winnu Kaulus Jabeṣā ap-\npakṣch to Obsolu/ un gaweja tep-\ntinas Deenas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "13. Ta nomirre Sauls eeksch\nsawcem Grebkrēm / ko winsch\nprett to KUNGU bij darrijs/ ta\nKUNGA Wahṛda pehz/ ko tas\nne turreja. Ir ka winch to Sihl-\nneezi bij watzajs un meklejs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "14. Un ne bij to KUNGU wai-\nzajs/ tapehz nokawe winsch to/\nun greese to Walstibu pee Dah-\nwidu Isaja Dehlu.\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
